CONNECTIONS:-
| MQ-135 Pin | Arduino Pin | Description   |
| ---------- | ----------- | ------------- |
| VCC        | 5V          | Power         |
| GND        | GND         | Ground        |
| AO         | A0          | Analog output |


| LCD Pin  | Arduino Pin                 | Description          |
| -------- | --------------------------- | -------------------- |
| VSS      | GND                         | Ground               |
| VDD      | 5V                          | Power                |
| V0       | Middle pin of Potentiometer | Contrast             |
| RS       | 12                          | Register Select      |
| RW       | GND                         | Ground               |
| E        | 11                          | Enable               |
| D4       | 5                           | Data                 |
| D5       | 4                           | Data                 |
| D6       | 3                           | Data                 |
| D7       | 2                           | Data                 |
| A (LED+) | 5V                          | LCD Backlight        |
| K (LED-) | GND                         | LCD Backlight Ground |


CODE:-

#include <LiquidCrystal.h>

LiquidCrystal lcd(12, 11, 5, 4, 3, 2);
int mq135Pin = A0;
int sensorValue;

void setup() {
  lcd.begin(16, 2);
  lcd.print("Air Quality:");
}

void loop() {
  sensorValue = analogRead(mq135Pin);
  lcd.setCursor(0, 1);
  lcd.print(sensorValue);
  lcd.print("   ");
  delay(1000);
}
